<p><i>No debugger warnings should be shown at any time.</i></p>
<ol>
<li>On startup verify that:
<ul>
<li>Tic Tac Toe Board is displayed
</ul></li>
<li>Play a game where X wins and verify that:
<ul>
<li>the message "Player X has won!" is displayed in a fixed modal window
<li>A red line connects the three winning squares
<li>clicking the ok button clears the board and the dialog
</ul></li>
<li>Play a game where O wins and verify that:
<ul>
<li>the message "Player O has won!" is displayed in a fixed modal window
<li>A red line connects the three winning squares
<li>clicking the ok button clears the board and the dialog
</ul></li>
<li>Play a game where neither wins and verify that:
<ul>
<li>the message "Nobody wins." is displayed in a fixed modal window
<li>no red lines are visible
<li>clicking the ok button clears the board and the dialog
</ul></li>
</ol>
